<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Booking Confirmation</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #f9f9f9; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 40px auto; background-color: #fff; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; border: 1px solid #eee; }
    h2 { color: #333; }
    .details { margin: 20px 0; }
    .details p { margin: 5px 0; }
    .highlight { font-weight: bold; color: #007BFF; }
    .footer { margin-top: 30px; font-size: 12px; color: #999; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Hello {{name}},</h2>
    <p>Thank you for your booking! Here are your booking details:</p>

    <div class="details">
      <p><span class="highlight">Booking ID:</span> {{bookingId}}</p>
      <p><span class="highlight">Hotel:</span> {{hotelName}}</p>
      <p><span class="highlight">Hotel Address:</span> {{hotelAddress}}</p>
      <p><span class="highlight">Room Type:</span> {{roomType}}</p>
      <p><span class="highlight">Price:</span> Rs{{price}}</p>
      <p><span class="highlight">Check-in Date:</span> {{checkInDate}}</p>
      <p><span class="highlight">Check-out Date:</span> {{checkOutDate}}</p>
      <p><span class="highlight">Total Guests:</span> {{totalGuests}}</p>
    </div>

    <p>We hope you enjoy your stay! If you have any questions, feel free to contact our support team.</p>

    <p>Thanks,<br/>Hotel Booking Team</p>

    <div class="footer">
      <p>This is an automated message. Please do not reply.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
